<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8">
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    </head>
    <body style="margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #081120; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif; color: #e2e8f0;">
        <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background-color: #081120;">
            <tr>
                <td align="center" style="padding: 40px 16px; background:
                    radial-gradient(circle at top, rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.18), transparent 36%),
                    radial-gradient(circle at bottom right, rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.10), transparent 30%),
                    #081120;">
                    <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="max-width: 640px; background-color: #0f172a; border: 1px solid rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.14); border-radius: 20px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 24px 80px rgba(2, 6, 23, 0.45);">
                        <tr>
                            <td style="height: 8px; background: linear-gradient(90deg, #10b981 0%, #22c55e 50%, #06b6d4 100%);"></td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td align="center" style="padding: 34px 28px 18px 28px; background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.15) 0%, rgba(15, 23, 42, 0) 100%);">
                                <div style="display: inline-block; padding: 10px 14px; border-radius: 999px; border: 1px solid rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.18); background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.8); font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #86efac; margin-bottom: 18px;">SmartRace</div>
                                <h1 style="margin: 0; font-size: 30px; line-height: 1.15; font-weight: 800; color: #ffffff; letter-spacing: -0.03em;">Compte validé</h1>
                                <p style="margin: 14px 0 0 0; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.6; color: #cbd5e1; max-width: 520px;">Bonjour {{ user.fullName || user.pseudo }}, votre compte est maintenant actif. Vous pouvez vous connecter et profiter de SmartRace.</p>
                            </td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td style="padding: 10px 28px 34px 28px;">
                                <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.72); border: 1px solid rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.14); border-radius: 18px;">
                                    <tr>
                                        <td style="padding: 28px 26px;">
                                            <p style="margin: 0 0 18px 0; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.7; color: #e2e8f0;">Un administrateur a approuvé votre profil. Vous pouvez désormais accéder à votre espace personnel et suivre les actualités de l’événement.</p>
                                            <div style="text-align: center; margin: 28px 0;">
                                                <a href="{{ loginUrl }}" style="display: inline-block; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #10b981 0%, #06b6d4 100%); color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; padding: 14px 28px; border-radius: 14px; font-weight: 700; font-size: 15px; box-shadow: 0 12px 28px rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.28);">Se connecter</a>
                                            </div>
                                            <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin-top: 22px; border: 1px solid rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.22); background: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.08); border-radius: 16px;">
                                                <tr>
                                                    <td style="padding: 16px 18px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.7; color: #86efac;">Bonne nouvelle: votre compte est prêt, vous n’avez rien d’autre à faire.</td>
                                                </tr>
                                            </table>
                                        </td>
                                    </tr>
                                </table>
                            </td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td style="padding: 18px 28px 28px 28px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.6; color: #64748b; border-top: 1px solid rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.12);">© 2026 SmartRace. Tous droits réservés.</td>
                        </tr>
                    </table>
                </td>
            </tr>
        </table>
    </body>
</html>
